We didn't have a ton of high level spells as we only got to clear half the Robe/BP area of Growth, and none of the named mobs.  We did however, get Occlusion of Sound for Muzikal, Gift of Insight for Scyllithe, and 13 other spells that were given away as random gifts and helpful bonuses to people's alts and guildmates.<br>
